<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Контакты | VR Heaven</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Свяжитесь с нами для аренды VR-шлема. Доступны в Telegram, WhatsApp, Авито.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body class="contact-page">

    <header class="header">
        <div class="container header__container" style="justify-content: center;">
            <div class="header__brand">
                <img src="logo.jpg" alt="Логотип" class="header__logo">
                <span class="header__title color-polar-white">VR Heaven</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="hero section-gap text-center" style="min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding-top: 80px;">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 600px;">
            <h1 class="text-display color-polar-white mb-4">Мы на связи</h1>
            <p class="text-body color-ash-gray" style="margin-bottom: 64px;">Выберите удобный способ связи, чтобы задать вопросы или забронировать шлем.</p>
            
            <div class="contact-grid mb-4">
                <a href="https://t.me/VrHeaven" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-contact btn-primary">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"></line><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"></polygon></svg>
                    Telegram
                </a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/79130692006" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-contact btn-primary">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"></path></svg>
                    WhatsApp
                </a>
                
                <a href="https://max.ru/u/f9LHodD0cOJNKJinB0NgOWQzlset9G4_n6e4eqzURC70fYM0fG3kdorubDg" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-contact btn-secondary">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg>
                    Max
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.avito.ru/novosibirsk/predlozheniya_uslug/arenda_vr_ochkov_oculus_quest_3s_7735645743" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-contact btn-secondary">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
                    Авито Профиль
                </a>
            </div>

            <a href="tel:+79130692006" id="trigger-call-modal" class="btn-contact btn-primary btn-full-width mb-4">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-subheading color-polar-white">+7-913-069-20-06</span>
            </a>

            <div class="mt-12">
                <!-- Кнопка "На главную" унифицирована и переведена в капс -->
                <a href="index.html" class="btn-contact btn-secondary" style="display: inline-flex; text-transform: uppercase;">На главную</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div id="call-modal" class="modal-overlay" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog card">
            <h3 class="text-heading-sm color-polar-white" style="text-transform: none; font-weight: 700 !important;">Позвонить нам?</h3>
            <div style="margin: 24px 0 40px 0;"> <!-- Увеличен отступ снизу -->
                <p class="text-body color-ash-gray">Вы собираетесь совершить звонок на номер</p>
                <div style="margin-top: 16px;">
                    <strong class="color-polar-white text-heading-sm">+7-913-069-20-06</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-actions">
                <button class="btn-contact btn-secondary" id="call-cancel">Отмена</button>
                <a href="tel:+79130692006" class="btn-contact btn-primary" id="call-confirm">Позвонить</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>